{"tid":1956531,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"4刀賊元朗搶車逃走　警窮追至大埔開槍擒賊","createTime":"2020-04-03T08:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T14:33:43.000Z","uid":3893,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"38599a88979ca60682451092e4817042b836798a","tid":1956531,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fuXM2wC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfuXM2wC.jpg&h=fe07fedd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元朗下白泥發生搶車劫案。今午(3日)3時許，一名男子在下白泥稔灣路一間士多對開，突然有4名男子撲出，部分人手持利刀朝他施襲，事主捱刀受傷淌血，群煞逞兇後跳上事主的私家車，繼而絕塵逃去，事主其後負傷報案。<br />\n警方接報立即展開捷進行動，在各個主要交通幹道設置路障，留意可疑車輛蹤影。新界北總區交通部執行及管制組特遣隊及後於新田公路發現該車，立即尾隨追截，窮追至大埔太和邨一個巴士站將之截停，當場拘捕4人。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">消息指，警方在展開拘捕行動期間一度開槍。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d11bd831243e24e64665bc2bea4d66d45ad8d88d","tid":1956531,"uid":158755,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:50:29.000Z","msg":"流浮山刀手終於出現<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過只係去到下白泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4643a6d1089fdbc68ca0545c1f16777311664c2","tid":1956531,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:51:09.000Z","msg":"「解悶工廠」 點解還押抗爭者仲睇到連登？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1956428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1956428</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d80f5d89e6a17d4114aa93476adfe76b28476855","tid":1956531,"uid":2656,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:51:17.000Z","msg":"郁d就開槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea640f1c94aa96e110fec0347b98113a33e81474","tid":1956531,"uid":78392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:51:58.000Z","msg":"自己人！"},{"pid":"193beb926e63e7f66ec312877d7b51ab8a761c1d","tid":1956531,"uid":48334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d80f5d89e6a17d4114aa93476adfe76b28476855","tid":1956531,"uid":2656,"lik